						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Disch wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Some old mappers doccuments available on the NESdev main page could give more percise information thant the wiki.</div><br /><br />*cough*cough*<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.romhacking.net/docs/362/">http://www.romhacking.net/docs/362/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />&lt;/plug&gt;</div>
<br />
<br />I read your documents and nowhere in mapper 04 (MMC3) does it mention if the CHR bank selected is switched by 1k increment or not.  Did I miss something in it?  Or maybe it written indirectly and I didn't saw the nuance about it?</div>

